    <summary>Local-first reader and vocabulary trainer for language learners.</summary>
    <description>Word Hunter is a local-first reader, vocabulary trainer, and language-learning workspace. Read real texts, click words to save them together with their context, and review vocabulary with spaced repetition while keeping control of your data.</description>
